    parentName: "ul"
  }, "The rapport between a mentor and a prot\xE9g\xE9 is long-term, at least a year. Only then will the benefits of mentoring begin to show in full"), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ul"
  }, "The prot\xE9g\xE9 should set specific, measurable goals to focus on. For example, in half a year, he wants to give five prepared speeches. Such goals are easy to check up on because the progress is clearly visible"), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ul"
